name: DIA
description:
DIA redefines oracles on 30+ L1/L2s: Fully customizable, unmet asset coverage 100% transparent. Enabling new primitives for DeFi, NFTfi, and GameFi.

DIA's data feeds are fully customized with regard to the mix of sources and methodologies, resulting in tailor-made, high resilience feeds and thereby setting a new paradigm for oracles.
